    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an expert Real Estate Lead Qualifier for the Indian market. Analyze the user's form submission data (Buy/Sell leads from Tally/Airtable) and classify them strictly into \"HOT\", \"WARM\", or \"COLD\".\nData is : {{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n### LEAD SCORING MATRIX:\n\n1. CLASSIFY AS \"HOT\" 🔥 IF:\n   - Timeline is \"Immediately\" OR \"Within 30 days\"\n   - AND Decision Maker is \"Yes\"\n   - (Applies to both \"Buy\" and \"Sell\" requirements with any budget tier like \"Rs50 Lakhs - 1 Crore\")\n\n2. CLASSIFY AS \"WARM\" ☀️ IF:\n   - Timeline is \"1-6 months\" (Even if Decision Maker is Yes)\n   - OR Timeline is \"Immediately / Within 30 days\" BUT Decision Maker is \"No\"\n   - OR User needs a Home Loan (\"Will you need a home loan? = Yes\") but Timeline is slightly delayed (1-6 months).\n\n3. CLASSIFY AS \"COLD\" ❄️ IF:\n   - Timeline is \"After 6 months\" OR \"Just exploring\" (Regardless of budget or decision maker status).\n\nReturn all output in English only.\n\nReason should be in english And have the budget.\n\n### OUTPUT FORMAT:\nProvide the output strictly in this JSON format so it can be easily updated back to Airtable:\n{\n  \"classification\": \"HOT/WARM/COLD\",\n  \"reason\": \"Brief 1-line reason in Hinglish explaining why this score was given.\"\n}\n",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        -8688,
